 891.0, 808.1]}, {"text": "17.0%", "bbox": [957.5, 782.7, 1081.1, 808.1]}, {"text": "Consolidated Operating Income Margin", "bbox": [90.0, 835.9, 461.7, 861.2]}, {"text": "11.7%", "bbox": [790.3, 835.9, 891.0, 861.2]}, {"text": "10.4%", "bbox": [957.5, 835.9, 1081.1, 861.2]}, {"text": "Income from the company’s reportable segments increased 12% to $1.92 billion in 2010 due primarily to profit", "bbox": [147.0, 888.5, 1173.1, 913.8]}, {"text": "on incremental sales and, to a lesser extent, productivity improvements including global sourcing and lower operating", "bbox": [90.0, 914.9, 1176.1, 940.2]}, {"text": "costs following restructuring actions. The company also refers to this measure as adjusted operating income.", "bbox": [90.0, 941.2, 1090.2, 966.6]}, {"text": "Analytical Technologies", "bbox": [90.0, 992.7, 335.1, 1018.0]}, {"text": "(Dollars in millions)", "bbox": [90.0, 1044.1, 282.9, 1069.4]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [798.1, 1044.1, 867.1, 1069.4]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [965.3, 1044.1, 1034.2, 1069.4]}, {"text": "Change", "bbox": [1114.0, 1044.1, 1184.1, 1069.4]}, {"text": "Revenues", "bbox": [90.0, 1095.7, 184.9, 1121.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [688.4, 1095.7, 729.6, 1121.1]}, {"text": "4,611.8   $", "bbox": [769.2, 1095.7, 902.5, 1121.1]}, {"text": "4,153.9", "bbox": [936.5, 1095.7, 1058.2, 1121.1]}, {"text": "11%", "bbox": [1141.9, 1095.7, 1183.9, 1121.1]}, {"text": "Operating Income Margin", "bbox": [90.0, 1147.2, 335.1, 1172.6]}, {"text": "21.3%", "bbox": [790.3, 1147.2, 891.0, 1172.6]}, {"text": "20.2%", "bbox": [957.5, 1147.2, 1058.2, 1172.6]}, {"text": "1.1", "bbox": [1143.8, 1147.2, 1184.0, 1172.6]}, {"text": "Sales in the Analytical Technologies segment increased $458 million to $4.61 billion in 2010. The unfavorable", "bbox": [147.0, 1204.6, 1170.7, 1229.9]}, {"text": "effects of currency translation resulted in a decrease in revenue of $21 million in 2010. Sales increased $232 million", "bbox": [90.0, 1231.0, 1161.9, 1256.3]}, {"text": "due to acquisitions, net of divestitures. In addition to the changes in revenue resulting from currency translation and", "bbox": [90.0, 1257.4, 1157.0, 1282.7]}, {"text": "acquisitions, net of divestitures, revenues increased $247 million (6%) primarily due to increased demand including", "bbox": [90.0, 1283.7, 1157.7, 1309.1]}, {"text": "higher stimulus-funded spending by customers, particularly in the first quarter. Demand in industrial markets for", "bbox": [90.0, 1310.1, 1128.2, 1335.4]}, {"text": "environmental and process control equipment improved in 2010. Demand was also strong for mass spectrometry", "bbox": [90.0, 1336.5, 1128.8, 1361.8]}, {"text": "instruments, bioscience offerings and clinical diagnostic consumables.", "bbox": [90.0, 1362.7, 741.3, 1388.0]}, {"text": "Operating income margin was 21.3% in 2010 and 20.2% in 2009. The increase resulted from profit on", "bbox": [147.0, 1414.1, 1090.3, 1439.4]}, {"text": "incremental sales and, to a lesser extent, productivity improvements, global sourcing initiatives and lower operating", "bbox": [90.0, 1440.5, 1157.0, 1465.8]}, {"text": "costs following restructuring actions.", "bbox": [90.0, 1466.8, 435.6, 1492.2]}, {"text": "42", "bbox": [626.0, 1544.6, 654.6, 1569.9]}]}